-Mw4XkxqdYBsnbbTN_kq.text: According to an update from the official Saint Paul Police Department Twitter Account, the woman suffered fatal injuries in the shooting.

-Mw4qa0xdk4uuMAOyDOP.text: According to an official report from the Saint Paul Police Department, medics rushed the woman to a hospital where she was later pronounced deceased. Multiple units are investigating the scene as they work to gather evidence. No arrests have been made and anyone with information is asked to call 651-266-5650.

nib.text:
A woman was fatally shot in Payne/Phalen Wednesday evening, officials said. 

Emergency responders responded to a report of a shooting in the 100 block of Payne Avenue just before 7 p.m.

Upon arrival, police discovered a woman inside a car who had been shot.

According to the SPPD, the woman was fatally wounded in the shooting. 

Homicide detectives are investigating. 

No arrests were reported.
